  "original_title": "LITRO gas distribution to resume today in Colombo, suburbs",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "LITRO gas distribution to resume today in Colombo, suburbs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "LITRO Gas Lanka Ltd has annouced that the distribution of cooking gas will resume today in Colombo and suburbs while distribution in other areas will be from Wednesday (13).",
        "LITRO Lanka said the maximum retail price of a 12.5 kg gas cylinder in Colombo is Rs. 4,910 and requested consumers not to buy gas paying higher prices or from other parties.",
        "It also requested the consumers to produce their electricity bill for the month of May as proof of identity when purchasing\u00a0 gas cylinders so as to prevent unnecessary hoarding of stocks.",
        "The company further said that information pertaining to the distribution centres will be made public through its social media and the LITRO Lanka's website."
      ],
